*波士顿地区：192,017（总人口的3.3%）<ref name=stats2>{{cite web| title = Census 2000- Population of European-American and other ethnic groups in major American metropolitan areas| url= http://www.euroamericans.net/metropolitan.htm|accessdate = 2007-02-12}}</ref>
*大纽纽约、新泽西和康涅狄格州：129,865（总人口的0.6%）<ref name="stats2"/>
